title: Avatar: The Legend of Korra - Book 1 (Pocket edition MP4) - Full
description:
A pocket edition of Avatar: Legend of Korra, specifically for tablets and mobile phones, or if you are low on bandwidth. For if you're going on vacation and want to have something to watch. It is only 623MB for the entire season. 

Resolution: 720x480
File size: 52mb per episode (623mb total)
Length: 24 min per episode (288min total)
Container: MP4
Video codec: x264
Audio codec: AAC
Audio quality: 92kbit/s stereo
Video quality: 200kbit/s (avg)
Encoded with 2 pass for optimal quality/space

The quality is actually pretty decent, but dont expect top quality. It is meant to save space.
